{"tid":1434454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] 趁住和你飛2.0，不如試吓搞五罷","createTime":"2019-08-08T19:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T20:03:21.000Z","uid":149210,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6c48fa7e00b3cc17c5462c414c075c9deba7c585","tid":1434454,"uid":149210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:12:46.000Z","msg":"朋友借account post︰<br />\n罷工、罷市、罷學、罷買之外，其實可以加多個「罷遊」！ 講緊嘅係發揮香港人好客精神，多啲關心訪港旅客安全。依家香港警隊已經完全失控，再加上鄉黑恐襲，如果旅客覺得唔安全就未必留喺香港啦。澳洲已經帶頭發出旅遊警告啦，香港咁依靠旅遊業，罷遊可以為香港經濟帶來壓力，逼政府正視市民五大訴求！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kY2CsiF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkY2CsiF.png&h=d02d20e0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUG7Pw1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUG7Pw1.png&h=f48d661a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sYE5Bb3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsYE5Bb3.png&h=22571a5e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RLCnDqp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRLCnDqp.png&h=50f7a244&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28e7463ae5e991c358564ead762b8d595486f0d6","tid":1434454,"uid":149210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:20:23.000Z","msg":"試吓十連先"},{"pid":"b51e8b7cadd30edbe902d75093ac1e98365c8e22","tid":1434454,"uid":149210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:20:48.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"eccffb1413c464f32b0bb96c61375bb74024abe0","tid":1434454,"uid":149210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:21:02.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"476ee51e59c77535eaca134112c9ed41b200d1e7","tid":1434454,"uid":149210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:21:27.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"f7f210c337a2a39aa1094b78bc6475f4e2283ff5","tid":1434454,"uid":149210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,